{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, in legal or financial contexts, the dissemination of incorrect information can result in poor decision-making with far-reaching consequences.",
    "Therefore, enhancing the factual accuracy of LLMs is essential to ensure their safe and effective deployment across various domains.",
    "One promising approach to improving the factual accuracy of LLMs is through Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG).",
    "RAG integrates retrieval mechanisms with generative models, thereby allowing the LLM to access and incorporate relevant information from external data sources during the generation process.",
    "By doing so, it enhances the model's ability to provide accurate and up-to-date responses."
  ]
}